English: In the beginning of the war they mostly travelled on top of the sea, but as radar began developing and becoming more accurate the submarines were forced to go under water to avoid being seen.

Turkish: Amerika Birleşik Devletleri Jeoloji Araştırmaları Kurumu uluslararası deprem haritası, İzlanda'da önceki hafta deprem olmadığını gösterdi. 
English: Turkey is surrounded by the Mediterranean Sea: the Black Sea to the north, the Aegean Sea to the south and the Sea of Marmara to the west.
